<br>
It is YOUR responsibility to:<br>
<br>
a) prove an existing rule is inadequate<br>
b) prove an existing rule is flawed<br>
c) prove an existing rule is unneeded<br>
d) show that a new rule is needed<br>
e) show that clarification is needed<br>
<br>
Also, you must:<br>
<br>
a) give alternatives of a &quot;better way&quot;<br>
b) give alternatives of a more &quot;correct&quot; way<br>
c) give evidence/examples of how these are really better/correct<br>
d) gather support<br>
<br>
<br>
So far, your arguments have been:<br>
<br>
1) I don't like rotations because they make me wait<br>
2) I think my guild can gather and kill the mob faster than other guilds so we should get the lion's share<br>
3) I don't like to share with others<br>
4) Therefore, the mobs should be FFA<br>
