<br>
1) To give smaller guilds a way to access content that they could access invidually together (keep in mind that key quests now flag up to 6 people at a time...)<br>
<br>
2) To keep the &quot;advancement by merit&quot; as opposed to advancement by overwhelming force in progression through POP.<br>
<br>
3) To ensure that there is a clear dictum on what can be team killed and what cannot. Only three mobs were named.<br>
